Steadfast Income REIT, Inc. Key Developments

Steadfast Income REIT, Inc. Announces Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the First Quarter Ended March 31, 2017
May 10 17
Steadfast Income REIT, Inc. announced unaudited consolidated earnings results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2017. For the quarter, the company reported total revenues of $54.280 million compared to $52.606 million a year ago. Net loss was $5.644 million or $0.07 basic and diluted per share compared to $3.618 million or $0.05 basic and diluted per share a year ago. FFO was $12.308 million compared to $13.329 million a year ago. MFFO was $12.628 million compared to $13.675 million a year ago. Net operating income was $28.276 million compared to $28.343 million a year ago. Net cash provided by operating activities was $10.9 million compared to $11.9 million for the three months ended March 31, 2016.


Steadfast Income REIT, Inc. Announces Consolidated Earnings Results for the Fourth Quarter and Full Year Ended December 31, 2016
Mar 16 17
Steadfast Income REIT, Inc. announced consolidated earnings results for the fourth quarter and full year ended December 31, 2016. For the full year, the company announced total revenues of $218,237,532 compared to $209,390,658 for the same period a year ago. Loss from continuing operations was $25,579,651 compared to $13,024,358 for the same period a year ago. Net loss was $25,579,651 compared to $13,024,358 for the same period a year ago. Loss per common share basic and diluted was $0.34 compared to $0.18 for the same period a year ago. FFO was $43,933,833 compared to $52,615,838 for the same period a year ago. MFFO was $49,117,817 compared to $55,143,904 for the same period a year ago. Reported net cash provided by operating activities of $54.3 million compared to $51.4 million for the year ended December 31, 2015. Net operating income was $113,675,575 compared to $112,345,930 for the same period a year ago.


For the quarter, the company announced net loss of $4,223,102 compared to $2,685,557 for the same period a year ago. Net operating income was $28,982,379 compared to $28,856,935 for the same period a year ago.


Steadfast Income REIT Inc. Reports Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the Third Quarter and Nine Months Ended September 30, 2016
Nov 14 16
Steadfast Income REIT Inc. reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the third quarter and nine months ended September 30, 2016. For the quarter, the company reported total revenues of USD 56,371,925 compared to USD 53,166,421 a year ago. Net loss was USD 9,699,187 or USD 0.13 per basic and diluted share compared to USD 3,603,728 or USD 0.05 per basic and diluted share a year ago. MFFO was USD 11,683,363 compared to USD 13,626,060 a year ago. FFO was USD 7,860,754 compared to USD 12,892,658 a year ago. Net operating income was USD 28,234,520 compared to USD 27,961,843 a year ago. 

For the nine months, the company reported total revenues of USD 163,301,458 compared to USD 156,461,523 a year ago. Net loss was USD 21,356,546 or USD 0.28 per basic and diluted share compared to USD 10,338,802 or USD 0.14 per basic and diluted share a year ago. MFFO was USD 35,996,018 compared to USD 40,624,771 a year ago. FFO was USD 30,367,439 compared to USD 38,493,910 a year ago. Net operating income was USD 84,389,684 compared to USD 82,992,328 a year ago. Net cash provided by operating activities was USD 38.3 million compared to USD 36.7 million for the nine months ended September 30, 2015.


