steadfast income reit inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Real Estate
Sub-Industry: REIT
Steadfast Income Reit, Inc. provides real estate investment services. The Company provides diverse portfolio of real estate investments focused primarily on the multifamily sector, including stable, income producing, and value added properties. Steadfast Income Reit serves customers in the United States.




